WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.503 --> 00:00:01.651
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.651 --> 00:00:02.800
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:03.520
Day 55.

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:17.145
We just want to say thank you for joining us today, and thank you for clicking the like button and the notification button, and all the things you all do to help spread this gospel throughout the whole world.

00:00:17.145 --> 00:00:26.320
With all the algorithms and all the things that YouTube requires to promote your video, we appreciate your help; we really do.

00:00:26.853 --> 00:00:32.680
People are emailing Diana, freaking out about all the drones in New Jersey.

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.410
Folks, I told you it was coming.

00:00:35.410 --> 00:00:37.564
It's funny to us because we laugh about it.

00:00:37.564 --> 00:01:20.920
You know, when the Lord visited me on July 6, 2014, he took me out—I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body, y'all—but when I tell people this, they always look at me like I'm crazy.

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:40.660
Especially when I first had the experience and tried to tell the people at the church, they mocked me a lot.

00:01:41.609 --> 00:02:14.916
I tried to keep things to myself because after you get crushed by friends who think you're crazy when you're telling them what Jesus said to you, I was really persecuted heavily.

00:02:14.916 --> 00:02:25.320
So, I didn't talk about it for years.

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:57.040
Then the Lord told me, 'I want you to go on YouTube and tell them that I'm coming and what you saw in the Tribulation.

00:02:57.040 --> 00:03:01.400
' I said, 'Lord, they're not going to believe it.

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:12.896
' He said, 'Brandon, I want you to be obedient and do this.

00:03:12.896 --> 00:03:26.120
' One year goes by, two years, three years, and I was not obedient.

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:39.653
He said, 'I want you to do this,' so I said, 'Okay, Lord.

00:03:39.653 --> 00:04:08.439
' I put it up and got a couple thousand views, but I'd take it down because I didn't like the comment section.

00:04:08.439 --> 00:04:29.168
I didn't like what people were saying; I said, 'These people are mean.

00:04:29.168 --> 00:04:44.293
' So, he told me to put it back up, and I did.

00:04:44.293 --> 00:04:51.720
Lo and behold, here we are with almost a million and a half views on that one video warning you all what's coming.

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:58.170
It's not a shock to me.

00:04:58.170 --> 00:05:09.457
I told you they were going to use the drones.

00:05:17.130 --> 00:05:23.548
Ladies and gentlemen, this is just a practice run for what's coming.

00:05:23.548 --> 00:05:34.480
They're trying to get you used to it.

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:53.706
The Lord showed me the illustration of a frog being boiled in a pot.

00:05:54.022 --> 00:06:16.249
The temperature rises, and he doesn't even know he's being cooked because he adapts to the water until it's too late.

00:06:16.249 --> 00:06:52.349
That's what a lot of you are like: adapting to what you see on social media with the alien stuff and the fallen angel stuff.

00:06:52.349 --> 00:06:59.000
They're messing with it.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:28.160
It's a demonic spirit or some kind of sci-fi government stuff they're trying to adopt, like Project Blue Beam.

00:07:31.970 --> 00:07:40.857
They're trying to get you used to what they're going to do in the future.

00:07:40.857 --> 00:08:26.662
They know they can't do it as much in the next administration, so they're trying to dump it out there as fast as they can so people get used to it.

00:08:26.662 --> 00:08:45.800
They say it's in New Jersey, or it's Iranians—I don't know what it is.

00:08:45.800 --> 00:09:03.800
All I know is the Lord told me this was going to happen before he came.

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:33.491
After he comes for the Rapture of the church, this will be something that everybody sees in the sky all over the place.

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:52.200
It will be all over Oklahoma, Florida, France, Germany, Moscow, and throughout Africa and South America.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:10:01.470
Drones flying in the skies—thousands of them.

00:10:01.470 --> 00:10:12.404
They look like swarms of bees flying over the sky in the day, scanning the horizon, and you will hear them coming.

00:10:12.404 --> 00:10:25.504
It will sound like traffic in the air.

00:10:28.806 --> 00:10:34.320
I remember it when I was with the Lord.

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:57.987
Whenever I was in the Tribulation, I could hear them, and it sounded like bees in the far distance.

00:10:57.987 --> 00:11:27.529
It wasn't all the time, but they would scan in swarms, all in lines, just like what the Chinese government is doing right now.

00:11:38.166 --> 00:12:16.830
They're getting ready for a surveillance state so that whenever those who are left get the mark of the beast and want the one-world money system—the digital platform happening with crypto—those drones will scan your hand or your forehead and know if you have it.

00:12:33.959 --> 00:12:47.899
I'm trying to warn you and yell as loud as I can, just like Paul Revere in the midnight hour, telling people the British were coming.

00:13:05.351 --> 00:13:11.120
As history tells us, he was trying to get the Minutemen to get ready to fight in the battle.

00:13:11.120 --> 00:13:47.120
I'm telling you, just like Paul Revere's warning, I'm running through the midnight hour right now telling you that Jesus is coming.

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:52.462
A lot of you are asleep and won't even wake up when you hear it.

00:13:52.462 --> 00:14:17.639
I'm riding through there as loud as I can, telling y'all to get ready because you're asleep.

00:14:23.387 --> 00:14:32.359
It's time for you to wake up today.

00:14:32.359 --> 00:14:56.419
The signs of the times are all around us, with Damascus falling and things going on in Syria.

00:15:02.668 --> 00:15:08.859
I warned you a great acceleration of war was coming.

00:15:08.859 --> 00:15:18.887
You see on the news that the drones are coming.

00:15:18.887 --> 00:15:31.938
There are going to be a lot of them.

00:15:46.965 --> 00:16:03.948
They're getting you ready and desensitizing you so you won't reject it when they start doing it a little at a time.

00:16:10.936 --> 00:16:23.152
It's easy to swallow that way, but hard when it's forced down everyone's throat at once.

00:16:23.152 --> 00:16:38.920
I warned you about the earthquakes happening in the New Madrid fault—seven in one day.

00:16:38.920 --> 00:16:48.169
Isn't that an interesting number?

00:16:48.169 --> 00:17:00.565
Seven, not six or eight, in a 24-hour period.

00:17:16.628 --> 00:17:17.240
That's a supernatural number: the number of completion.

00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:25.785
What is the Lord trying to speak through earthquakes?

00:17:25.785 --> 00:18:04.600
He told you there would be earthquakes in diverse places and fearful sights, that men's hearts would fail them for fear of what is coming on the earth.

00:18:04.600 --> 00:18:17.840
I told you it won't just be about war, politics, and finances.

00:18:17.840 --> 00:18:43.360
I told you a couple of videos back that we would see signs in the heavens, and now the drones are here.

00:18:43.360 --> 00:18:51.474
This is just the beginning.

00:18:51.474 --> 00:19:08.373
Then we're going to start to see 'alien' stuff, and a great deception is coming.

00:19:08.600 --> 00:19:27.970
A lot of people are going to take the bait, but smart people will reject it.

00:19:27.970 --> 00:19:36.850
Don't be a dumb fish or a sheep.

00:19:36.850 --> 00:19:55.280
We'll see asteroids and comets that are really going to freak people out.

00:19:55.280 --> 00:20:26.809
If you go back to Oral Roberts's visitation, the 'Great Wake-Up Call' from 2004—talking twenty-one years later—I believe it's about to take place.

00:20:26.809 --> 00:20:34.280
People say, 'Was that COVID?

00:20:34.280 --> 00:20:45.320
' No, it's a sign in the heavens.

00:20:45.320 --> 00:20:52.679
It was something loud and deafening.

00:20:56.209 --> 00:21:05.760
The Lord told me we're going to start seeing things.

00:21:05.760 --> 00:21:12.977
We're going to see volcanoes.

00:21:12.977 --> 00:21:23.036
I warned you about the one in Italy.

00:21:39.617 --> 00:21:42.788
I saw a 'canary in the coal mine' situation with gases from there.

00:21:42.788 --> 00:22:16.840
I saw canaries falling and dying, and the Lord warned me there would be poisonous gases coming from the earth, wiping out hundreds of thousands of people.

00:22:22.925 --> 00:22:33.195
I saw 300,000 plus people perishing when this gas comes out of the ground.

00:22:33.195 --> 00:22:52.999
I saw a tsunami wave wiping out the coast of Italy because of the earthquake when this volcano goes off.

00:22:57.023 --> 00:23:05.825
That hasn't happened yet; it has been delayed, but I believe the Lord told me this was one of the major things coming.

00:23:05.825 --> 00:23:16.809
I even told you the area it was going to happen in.

00:23:16.809 --> 00:23:48.590
I told you about the asteroid I saw falling from the sky that was massive—it hit by San Juan, Puerto Rico, and flooded all of Miami with a massive tsunami.

00:24:05.662 --> 00:24:05.978
Is that during the Tribulation?

00:24:16.990 --> 00:24:17.200
I don't know.

00:24:30.270 --> 00:24:30.605
The Lord didn't say; he just told me it was coming.

00:24:30.605 --> 00:24:46.120
Sometimes I see things years in advance, just like Kim Clement, whom everybody loves.

00:24:54.343 --> 00:24:56.457
He was a great man and very sharp.

00:24:56.457 --> 00:25:18.155
When Kim Clement and John Paul Jackson went home, the Lord said, 'Generals go home, son.

00:25:18.155 --> 00:25:44.000
' In war times, they go home, but he raises up another general to take the baton and warn his people.

00:25:44.000 --> 00:26:05.274
God's bringing up new leaders for this time, and I'm trying to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:26:05.274 --> 00:26:14.064
You're seeing it on the news every day.

00:26:14.064 --> 00:26:19.408
Now we see Damascus and Israel.

00:26:23.970 --> 00:26:33.183
For all you 'news hounds' sending me articles—thank you for helping.

00:26:33.183 --> 00:26:42.498
Diana skins over them and tells me what's happening.

00:26:45.135 --> 00:26:52.600
We see Israel saying they're going to strike nuclear facilities.

00:27:03.520 --> 00:27:10.879
I warned you they were going to strike the gas refineries and oil would go over $200 a barrel.

00:27:10.879 --> 00:27:16.300
This was part of the plan.

00:27:16.300 --> 00:27:49.359
It's not a pat on my back; I'm just doing my job as best I can to warn and yell as loud as I can that Jesus is coming.

00:27:49.359 --> 00:28:16.916
I tried to warn you yesterday to pray for Donald Trump and his kids because these people want to treat him like JFK.

00:28:16.916 --> 00:28:32.258
I try to be discreet, but sometimes you just have to be bold.

00:28:35.820 --> 00:28:36.056
This is serious.

00:28:36.056 --> 00:28:52.871
Pray for his children because as he touches this stuff, there is retaliation; every action brings another reaction.

00:28:52.871 --> 00:29:08.920
These people are dark, and they don't like it when you touch their agenda.

00:29:10.679 --> 00:29:20.112
The last administration was buddies with them.

00:29:25.553 --> 00:29:42.044
The head of it is the Devil, the puppet master controlling all these politicians, banking industries, and multi-billionaires like the Soroses and all of them.

00:29:42.044 --> 00:29:49.760
It's all about money, power, and influence.

00:29:49.760 --> 00:29:55.279
But God brings peace and joy.

00:29:55.279 --> 00:30:09.308
Financial gain comes when you are able to handle it so it won't destroy you.

00:30:17.120 --> 00:30:22.504
Get character so you can be an end-time harvester for the gospel.

00:30:22.504 --> 00:30:58.830
People like those who own Hobby Lobby or the man at Chick-fil-A before he passed away—I knew for a fact he sowed to a ministry I used to work for.

00:30:58.830 --> 00:31:20.899
He used to give fat checks and help them get TV time; he was a sower.

00:31:20.899 --> 00:31:39.360
And I know for a fact the Green family sowed because they bought my friend a church.

00:31:39.360 --> 00:31:57.120
Be like a warhorse that's not swayed by noises but moves only by the steady hand of the rider.

00:31:59.826 --> 00:32:07.200
I am filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:32:10.302 --> 00:32:12.899
I get corrected all the time because he's molding me.

00:32:12.899 --> 00:32:40.548
Sometimes he'll give me a certain instruction, and I'll say, 'Lord, I've been doing it this way for years,' but he says, 'As of today, don't do that.

00:32:40.548 --> 00:32:48.519
' If you do it anyway, that's disobedience.

00:32:48.519 --> 00:32:53.555
It's following the Commander-in-Chief.

00:32:53.555 --> 00:33:04.119
Even if it doesn't make sense, it's blind obedience.

00:33:04.119 --> 00:33:08.212
I'm not moved by circumstances.

00:33:11.640 --> 00:33:14.013
We're going to pray today.

00:33:14.013 --> 00:33:24.719
I'm interceding for Brandon and Sherry, who have had miscarriages.

00:33:24.719 --> 00:33:33.368
We stand with you today that those stop now.

00:33:33.368 --> 00:33:43.039
You'll have a baby in 2025; it will be a supernatural experience.

00:33:43.039 --> 00:33:58.640
This will be a year of the babies and supernatural fruit in your life.

00:33:58.640 --> 00:34:05.186
Father, we lift up President Trump.

00:34:07.788 --> 00:34:37.560
The demonic assignment sent to destroy his family, I speak to this in the name of Jesus and say, 'Satan, you will not take out his family.

00:34:37.560 --> 00:34:53.280
' You will not touch his marriage, his sons, his daughters, or his grandkids.

00:34:53.280 --> 00:35:11.780
We plead the blood of Jesus over our leadership, over our president-to-be, and over his wife.

00:35:24.120 --> 00:35:26.800
We call forth a renewing of the love they had for each other.

00:35:26.800 --> 00:35:55.055
I thank you, Father, that your angels are bearing them up in their hands lest they dash their foot against a stone.

00:36:02.897 --> 00:36:06.367
We believe there are secret service angels watching over them.

00:36:22.666 --> 00:36:22.959
I thank you, Lord, for supernatural wisdom on him like a Solomon.

00:36:22.959 --> 00:36:31.181
Now, Diana will pray for the babies.

00:36:40.353 --> 00:36:51.783
We have an email about Brandon and Sherry, who haven't been able to have a baby in 20 years.

00:36:55.980 --> 00:37:03.874
Father, right now we lift up this couple.

00:37:03.874 --> 00:37:15.960
Bless the fruit of their womb and their reproductive systems.

00:37:15.960 --> 00:37:35.136
We speak to the ovaries and the fallopian tubes right now; you will produce.

00:37:40.596 --> 00:37:40.884
We call for restoration.

00:37:40.884 --> 00:37:59.393
Your word says to be fruitful and multiply, and it's their heart's desire to have a child.

00:38:03.999 --> 00:38:15.114
I thank you, Father, that they will conceive and have a healthy baby.

00:38:15.114 --> 00:38:21.000
No more miscarriages in Jesus' name.

00:38:21.000 --> 00:38:27.360
Her vine will not cast its fruit before its time.

00:38:43.140 --> 00:38:43.470
We thank you that the embryo implants as it's supposed to.

00:38:43.470 --> 00:38:55.288
Womb, you accept that baby and carry it full term.

00:38:55.288 --> 00:38:58.640
Satan, no more.

00:38:58.640 --> 00:39:07.929
Release her and let her go right now.

00:39:07.929 --> 00:39:25.860
I'm believing God that she won't even have morning sickness or postpartum depression.

00:39:25.860 --> 00:39:34.880
We're standing for every single person.

00:39:34.880 --> 00:39:58.750
As you take your eyes off your need and pray for somebody else's, it brings forth your harvest.

00:39:58.750 --> 00:40:19.135
If the doctors said something doesn't work, you say, 'Ovaries, you line up.

00:40:19.135 --> 00:40:42.200
' If you need a new fallopian tube—the Father has body parts in his silos—nothing's too big.

00:40:42.200 --> 00:40:52.255
Speak to the sperm and the egg.

00:40:52.255 --> 00:41:04.886
No lazy sperm; be fast-forward thrusting and do your job.

00:41:04.886 --> 00:41:13.652
Your body ovulates like it's supposed to.

00:41:13.652 --> 00:41:28.413
He was wounded for our transgressions, and with his stripes, we are healed.

00:41:28.413 --> 00:41:47.593
He took the curse for us, so body, you line up with what the Word of God says.

00:41:47.593 --> 00:42:03.300
You speak to your mountain and say, 'I'm not dealing with ovulation problems.

00:42:03.300 --> 00:42:09.000
My womb is fertile.

00:42:09.000 --> 00:42:19.650
' 2025 will be the year of the baby.

00:42:19.650 --> 00:42:35.724
As for me and my house, we're going to have a good year.

00:42:35.724 --> 00:42:41.240
We're taking the land back.

00:42:41.240 --> 00:42:44.079
It's done.

00:42:44.079 --> 00:42:51.760
We have a relationship with the Lord.

00:42:51.760 --> 00:42:54.264
It's personal.

00:42:54.264 --> 00:42:59.127
When you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:42:59.127 --> 00:43:12.110
2025 is time to walk in victory—it's a victor mentality.

00:43:12.110 --> 00:43:18.079
We're more than conquerors.

00:43:18.079 --> 00:43:25.933
I speak even to the small things.

00:43:25.933 --> 00:43:32.533
Don't say, 'I'm so forgetful.

00:43:32.533 --> 00:43:42.070
' No, you have the mind of Christ.

00:43:54.030 --> 00:43:54.465
Don't say, 'That scared me to death.

00:43:54.465 --> 00:44:08.418
' You scare yourself by what you say out of your mouth.

00:44:08.418 --> 00:44:26.457
Put a tab in your Bible on the things you're believing for.

00:44:26.754 --> 00:44:37.480
The word will work if you work it.

00:44:37.480 --> 00:44:41.650
He made faith simple.

00:44:41.650 --> 00:45:03.821
My daughter Paisley raised a dog from the dead after it was squashed in the trash can.

00:45:05.440 --> 00:45:17.240
It took the faith of a child—she was only about six years old.

00:45:17.240 --> 00:45:30.871
A little mustard seed of faith will move a mountain.

00:45:30.871 --> 00:45:42.740
Father, we agree for healings and that people are made whole.

00:45:42.740 --> 00:45:51.140
You're delivered from sickness and disease.

00:46:00.373 --> 00:46:01.773
We believe for your finances and for better jobs.

00:46:12.639 --> 00:46:13.559
2025 will be a time that you thrive.

00:46:13.559 --> 00:46:20.359
It's time to 'thrive in '25.

00:46:20.359 --> 00:46:33.754
' It should be the greatest year you've ever lived.

00:46:33.754 --> 00:46:38.159
We serve a big God.

00:46:38.159 --> 00:46:55.386
He doesn't have to check a heavenly piggy bank to see if there's enough money.

00:46:55.386 --> 00:47:10.093
We call Elon Musk saved in Jesus' name.

00:47:10.093 --> 00:47:47.920
We pray for the war not to happen, though you showed me wars and rumors of wars that would lead into Ezekiel 38 and 39.

00:47:47.920 --> 00:47:58.715
Watch out for Taiwan.

00:47:58.715 --> 00:48:21.240
I've seen China attack and circle that island, but I believe for the believers there.

00:48:31.400 --> 00:48:43.350
We call forth a move of God in China, South Korea, Japan, the Philippines, and Vietnam.

00:48:43.350 --> 00:48:54.297
Take the blinders off regarding Buddha and false religions.

00:48:54.297 --> 00:49:18.640
When I was in heaven, the Lord showed me gold veins throughout Asia—that's his underground church.

00:49:18.640 --> 00:49:29.137
Communism will not be able to contain it.

00:49:29.137 --> 00:49:51.115
South Korea will go through refining, but there will be a great revival that spreads into North Korea.

00:50:04.539 --> 00:50:09.520
The Lord will deal with Kim Jong Un just like he did with Pharaoh.

00:50:09.520 --> 00:50:18.771
My Asian people have not been forgotten.

00:50:18.771 --> 00:50:25.080
He's seen your tears.

00:50:25.080 --> 00:50:34.040
David's are rising up and breaking those chains.

00:50:36.920 --> 00:50:42.880
The glory is coming to shake the world.

00:50:42.880 --> 00:50:47.160
San Juan, Puerto Rico and Cuba are coming to Jesus.

00:50:47.160 --> 00:50:55.815
Haiti will see the voodoo pushed back.

00:50:55.815 --> 00:51:00.012
Angel armies are coming.

00:51:00.012 --> 00:51:34.310
They will know the salvation in the Gospel of John, that God so loved the world that he gave his only begotten son.

00:51:34.310 --> 00:51:43.939
2025 will be a four-year window of reprieve.

00:51:43.939 --> 00:51:53.640
What are you going to do with that window?

00:51:53.640 --> 00:52:13.863
I saw revival taking place in Collinsville and Fort Worth, all along the I-35 corridor.

00:52:20.543 --> 00:52:34.547
I saw people in fields in tents, like a 'Holy Ghost Woodstock' with manifestations and healings.

00:52:34.547 --> 00:52:42.100
Even the unlikelys will get born again.

00:52:42.100 --> 00:52:48.294
Harvesters, get your hearts ready.

00:52:48.294 --> 00:53:04.820
We should be busting the doors down to get into church.

00:53:04.820 --> 00:53:12.400
Don't be stoic; come out charged.

00:53:16.418 --> 00:53:31.640
We need to create an atmosphere for the Holy Spirit in our houses through worship.

00:53:31.640 --> 00:53:44.750
I'm thankful for being born for such a time as this.

00:53:48.900 --> 00:53:53.320
You are an inferno, not just a little light.

00:54:06.640 --> 00:54:07.028
You can't be a part-time Christian fighting a full-time devil.

00:54:07.028 --> 00:54:18.240
We're believing for 100,000 people to pray every day.

00:54:21.160 --> 00:54:32.983
I know people are desperate, but don't give up on yourself.

00:54:32.983 --> 00:54:39.200
Joy comes in the morning.

00:54:51.020 --> 00:54:51.250
The storm won't last.

00:54:56.539 --> 00:55:00.680
You're on the one-yard line, fixing to make a touchdown.

00:55:07.120 --> 00:55:07.760
Push harder.

00:55:07.760 --> 00:55:13.685
Sing 'Because He Lives' to face tomorrow.

00:55:13.685 --> 00:55:22.499
Life is worth living just because he lives.

00:55:22.499 --> 00:55:23.475
We love you and pray for you.

00:55:25.533 --> 00:55:47.760
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:55:47.760 --> 00:55:53.988
God bless you all.

00:55:53.988 --> 00:56:21.032
We'll be here tomorrow for day 56.

00:56:21.032 --> 00:56:24.890
Bye-bye.
